.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-AGE-TOP10" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-age-top10 \- FEAT-2732 channel-age-top10 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-age-top10
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show the top 10 oldest channels sorted by short channel ID (which encodes block height).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBtop10_oldest\fR containing an array of channel objects.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
